### 测试 JSON 格式化接口
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/json/format
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json": "{\"name\":\"张三\",\"age\":18,\"hobbies\":[\"编程\",\"音乐\"]}"
}

### 测试错误的 JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/json/format
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json": "{name:张三,age:18}"
}

### Base64 编码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/base64/encode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello World"
}

### Base64 解码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/base64/decode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "base64": "SGVsbG8gV29ybGQ="
}

### MD5 加密
POST http://localhost:8080/api/crypto/md5/encrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "123456"
}

### SHA256 加密
POST http://localhost:8080/api/crypto/sha256/encrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "123456"
}

### URL 编码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/url/encode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "https://example.com/search?q=你好世界"
}

### URL 解码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/text/url/decode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "https%3A%2F%2Fexample.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C"
}